<div class="container">
  <p>To configure a repository to use this LFS server, add the following to the repository's <code>.gitconfig</code> file:</p>
  <pre>
  <code>[lfs]
      url = "{{.Config.Scheme}}://{{.Config.Host}}{{.Config.UrlContext}}/&lt;user&gt;/repo"
  </code>
  </pre>

  {{if eq .Config.Scheme "https"}}
  <p>Your server is configured to use https. If you're using self signed certificates, or are getting SSL errors, you can add the following to your <code>.gitconfig</code> file:</p>
  <pre>
  <code>[http]
      sslverify = false
  </code>
  </pre>
{{end}}
</div>
<br>
